VL  - 25
IS  - 2
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The impact of four grand strategies on the relative importance of seven organizational functions and the moderating effects of type of production system and perceived environmental uncertainty were examined. The strategic importance of organizational functions was found to vary by grand strategy. Type of production system and perceived environmental uncertainty showed weak moderating effects.
AB  - The impact of four grand strategies on the relative importance of seven organizational functions and the moderating effects of type of production system and perceived environmental uncertainty were examined. The strategic importance of organizational functions was found to vary by grand strategy. Type of production system and perceived environmental uncertainty showed weak moderating effects.
