T1  - Top Executive Locus of Control and Its Relationship to Strategy-Making, Structure, and Environment
AU  - Miller, Danny
AU  - Kets de Vries, Manfred F. R.
AU  - Toulouse, Jean-Marie
Y1  - 1982/06/01
PY  - 1982
